{"id":108973,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":8,"day":26}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"232","ytitle":"","mtitle":"弦与箭","ftitle":"","authors":["陈敬齐"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战慄的弦上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那闪光的箭紧张着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等候着你，手呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你轻轻的一发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行路人来了又去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光亮了又灭了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只一片风还依恋地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彷徨在欢乐的树梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让水拥抱你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让水亲吻你吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长年浮泛于生命之激流的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可爱的年青姑娘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着眼睛的倦意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双足的倦意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流浪人的琴声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘落在黄昏的窗上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘下所有的阳光，月光，星光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯烛与萤虫的微光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和圣洁的眼中那无际的澄光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回广漠的草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然一把野火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也照亮希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从战慄的弦上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪光的箭掠去了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急剧地送来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个最清脆的音响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四五·六·十一，夜客重庆。"}]}